":"#### Issue details\r\nA progress bar's knobBefore will not disappear when the Value is set to 0. Even after having made sure the minWidth of the knobBefore drawable was 0. \r\nThis issue seems to be related to c6b7119a53c94086ce04f07f62d2bf44f8cf0739\r\nWhile Testing I made a subclass of ProgressBar and reverted the changes for Math.max(bgBottomHeight, position); back to Math.max(Math.min(0, bgBottomHeight), position);  and Math.max(bgLeftWidth, position); back to Math.max(Math.min(0, bgLeftWidth), position);  and it began to work as expected.\r\n\r\n#### Reproduction steps/code\r\nMade a simple barebones project. Using a skin with a just a drawable for the background and knobBefore.\r\nProgressBar min/max, 0 to 50, value set to 0;\r\n\r\n#### Version of LibGDX and/or relevant dependencies\r\n1.9.12, 1.9.13, 1.9.14 and 1.10.0\r\n![progressbarrIssue](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/55356015/117995771-97f18000-b30f-11eb-947c-3a2e09626720.png)\r\n\r\n#### Please select the affected platforms\r\n- [x] Android\r\n- [x] iOS\r\n- [x] HTML/GWT\r\n- [x] Windows\r\n- [x] Linux\r\n- [x] MacOS\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"NathanSweet","id":434010,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQzNDAxMA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/434010?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/NathanSweet","html_url":"https://github.com/NathanSweet","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/NathanSweet/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/NathanSweet/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/NathanSweet/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/NathanSweet/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/NathanSweet/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/NathanSweet/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/NathanSweet/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/NathanSweet/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/